Package: rxref
Title: Tidy Utilities for RxNorm and NDC Resolution (API-first)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
	c(person(given = "Steven", family = "Smith", email = "ssmith@cop.ufl.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: A tidy, vectorized R interface to the RxNorm / RxNav API for resolving free-text drug strings, RxCUIs, and NDCs, retrieving core drug properties, and mapping identifiers in both directions.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/ssmithm/rxref
